# Pagecord

> A blog you'll actually keep updated.

Pagecord is an independent blogging platform for people who want to keep a personal blog alive. Publish wherever you like, from email, Obsidian, the editor, API, CLI, or your own scripts. Readers can follow by RSS or email. Free forever, with Premium available for custom domains, email subscribers, analytics, images, Obsidian, API, CLI, and more.

## Features
- Post by email (forward or compose to your blog)
- Rich text editor with images, tables, code blocks
- Obsidian, API, and CLI publishing
- Custom home page
- Themes, colors, custom CSS
- Tags and RSS feeds
- Email newsletter (weekly digest or per-post delivery to subscribers)
- Privacy-respecting analytics
- Custom domains
- Reply by email (readers can respond to posts)
- Full site HTML export
- Dynamic open graph images

